## What to Look For

### Orphaned Roles
Roles with no parent grant are unreachable from the standard hierarchy. Common causes:
- Data Product Setup was interrupted before wiring the hierarchy
- Roles created manually outside of the blueprint process
- Roles left over from deleted data products

### Excessive Depth
Hierarchies deeper than 5 levels make it difficult to reason about effective privileges. The standard Data Product Setup hierarchy is 4 levels deep: READ → WRITE → CREATE → ADMIN → SYSADMIN.

